{"tid":111890,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【罪大】SONY發表全新手機用CMOS，強化慢鏡效果。","createTime":"2017-02-07T17:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T07:27:21.000Z","uid":69439,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77f1450a79abbef9f295325109c9189bf00e8ccc","tid":111890,"uid":69439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T17:03:23.000Z","msg":"<strong>Sony 的新 CMOS 能拍出驚人的慢鏡頭效果</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">多一層 DRAM，讓你能用手機來拍 1080p @1,000fps 影片。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/2326716b4075f077cea07bb1075263a0/204905221/sony-high-speed-image-sensor-2017-02-07-05.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fhss%2Fstorage%2Fmidas%2F2326716b4075f077cea07bb1075263a0%2F204905221%2Fsony-high-speed-image-sensor-2017-02-07-05.jpeg&h=602ac38d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前比較常見的手機用 CMOS 大多為雙層式設計，而今天下午 Sony 發表了一款新品，首度引入了三層堆疊的結構。它在原有基礎上多加了一層 DRAM，換來的好處是大幅提升了讀取速度。具體來說，這款新感光元件可以在 1/120 秒的時間內拍下 19.3MP 的照片（用 Sony 的話來說「速度是普通產品的四倍」），如果是用在錄影上，它則能以 1080p 的解析度，進行最高 1,000fps 幀率的慢動作錄影。<br />\n<br />\n這種讀取速度能有效減少簾幕快門的「焦平面畸變」（或者更通俗一點說，果凍效應），避免因讀取先後而造成的運動物體垂直方向變形。從下面這組對比圖中，可以清楚地看出在 1/30 秒和 1/120 秒前提下，被攝車頭的形狀在照片中會呈現出怎樣的不同。而 Sony 的新組件就是為了達到後一種效果，便於使用者更好地拍攝運動物體。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/cd45965d159c05fd2f2d3deef823942f/204904849/sony-high-speed-image-sensor-2017-02-07-04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.aolcdn.com%2Fhss%2Fstorage%2Fmidas%2Fcd45965d159c05fd2f2d3deef823942f%2F204904849%2Fsony-high-speed-image-sensor-2017-02-07-04.jpg&h=fa37d155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除此之外，1080p 解析度下高達 1,000fps 的慢動作錄影能力，超高的幀率將目前的主流水準遠遠拋在了身後（Pixel 也只是能拍 120fps 而已）。廠方提供的示範影片，慢鏡頭的效果頗有大片的感覺，相信在實際應用中會受到許多用戶的青睞。另外，Sony 還表示這顆 CMOS 的高速讀取模式會自動按需開啟，而且他們還解決了在兩層結構間加入 DRAM 可能產生的噪聲問題。不過，目前還不確定該款產品將於何時被交到手機廠商手中，想用的話還是得多點耐心等一等囉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dFdU-JjypWs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdFdU-JjypWs&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=645f2376\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dFdU-JjypWs</a><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinese.engadget.com/2017/02/07/sonys-latest-sensor-shoots-ridiculous-slow-mo-video/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2017%2F02%2F07%2Fsonys-latest-sensor-shoots-ridiculous-slow-mo-video%2F&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=17e63730\" target=\"_blank\">http://chinese.engadget.com/2017/02/07/sonys-latest-sensor-shoots-ridiculous-slow-mo-video/</a>"},{"pid":"ec22b20922c29b55cafb3586384c63505d77035e","tid":111890,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:58:42.000Z","msg":"然後得64gb rom"},{"pid":"c179f64300cd3247bce6d7240ed0c94ceae0a494","tid":111890,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T02:33:27.000Z","msg":"大台經常會用嘅超慢鏡頭效果 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ae75376639e1780bdb10192f898a07aa342222","tid":111890,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>然後得64gb rom</blockquote><br />\n咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e3ddaf42a380bdd7e40a0fda8782a9c4a666a2","tid":111890,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T02:41:46.000Z","msg":"但sony手機影出黎既相都係咁油畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b311111e1379b8a07db17e21301832cdcf90f76b","tid":111890,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:50:14.000Z","msg":"交到去手機部門都係食撚屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8724421c1d987b1702f915567afbc694a9450c9b","tid":111890,"ui